content.rendered:
Directed by Sneha Taurani

Written by Dheeraj Rattan

Cast Sunny Kaushal (Jaggi Singh). Rukshar Dhillon (Simi Kohli (as Rukhsar Dhillon)). Shriya Pilgaonkar (Nimmo). Parmeet Sethi (Jaggi’s father). Samir Soni (Simi’s father).Chaitnya Sharma. Sheeba Chaddha (Simi’s mother). Jayati Bhatia (Jaggi’s Mother).Akarsh Khurana. Kamlesh Gill (Nimmo’s grandmother). Sarthak Kakar (Pappi). Swasti Kapur (Kiran). Mark Bennington (Henderson).Asha Arora.Radhika Bangia.Gaurav Beniwal.Avni Bhatia. Mahabir Bhullar (Kaptaan’s father).Govind Bisht.Gurjeet Singh Channi. Sandeep Chugh ((as Sandeep Chug)).Nitin Goyal.Naila Grewal.Ana Ilma. Emiko Ishii (Canada Team Leader). Goral Joshi (Harpriya).Tvisha Joshi. Gourav Kamboj (Pendu Club Dancer (as Gaurav Kamboj)). Seema Kaushal (Kaptaan’s mother). Balraj Singh Khehra (Nimmo’s Elder Brother (as Balraj Singh)). Jashan Singh Kohli (Cadet (as Jashn Kohli)).Nikhil Basant Kumar.Shereoshi Kumar. Mohit Mathur (Manish).Mohit Mathur.Minto.Priyanka Mitra.Chandar Mohan. Varun Narang (Judge-Bhangra Competition).Rishi Panchal. Ravinder Pawar (Lakha (as Ravindra Singh)).Rohan Prasad.Sarvi Rattan.Tejas Ravishankar. Sunit Razdan (Subedar Karim).Priyam Saha.Ashok Salaria. Swairaj Sandhu ((as Swaraj Sandhu)).Gautam Sharma.Sujeet Kumar Sharma.Harnimrat Singh Sidhu.Babalbir Singh.Harpal Singh.Kulwinder Singh.Sahaj Singh. Aklima Uddin (Dancer).Anjali Verma. Yorgo Glynatsis (Canada Team Dancer (uncredited)). Chandni Srivastava (Contestant (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Devanshu Asthana. Vighnesh Chendwankar. Karan Gill. Wahi Harsh. Pashan Jal. Salona Bains Joshi. Sonia Kanwar. Yogendra Mogre. Yogiraj Shetty. Shubh Shivdasani. Nishan Singh. Shantanu Tungare. Sanaya Irani Zohrabi

Production RSV
